fem.interFace

Interface IElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, INamedObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractElement, ConstantStrainTriangle, PlaneQuad4Iso, Quad4Iso, Triangle

    public interface IElement
extends INamedObject
    Interface which contains specific methods that are required by all finite elements.
    Author:
    Darren Sulon
